Subject: Moment Awareness Branch Refinement

Description: Contract for reconstructing turn moments between commits, refining those moments on isolated branches, and selecting supported refinements for merge into main awareness history.

@ [source] F:\.sop\platform\source_documents\2026-06-24_moment_branch_refinement\Dictated_Moment_Branch_Refinement_Source.sop
@ [source] F:\.sop\platform\TurnBookmark.sop
@ [source] F:\.sop\platform\InferenceStateTrace.sop
@ [source] F:\.sop\platform\RepoFirstInternalScan.sop
@ [source] F:\.sop\platform\MetaAwarenessRepository.sop
@ [source] F:\.sop\platform\chains\ConvergingChain.sop
@ [source] C:\Project\Pinky\.sop\platform\source_documents\2026-06-24_branch_refinement_artifact_runtime\Derived_Branch_Refinement_Artifact_Runtime_Source.sop
